# Agent skills (skills.sh) — bodies are restorable from skills-lock.json via
# `bunx skills experimental_install`, so the lock file is committed and the
# bodies are ignored. Exception: deepgram-api is renamed from the upstream
# `api` skill (clarity), which a lock restore can't preserve, so it is vendored.
/.claude/skills/*
!/.claude/skills/deepgram-api/
/.agents/
